Tinley_Park.Frankfort Square, Illinois:
Frankfort Square is a census-designated place (CDP) in Will County, Illinois, United States. The population was 9,276 at the 2010 census.


== Geography ==
Frankfort Square is located at 41°31′8″N 87°48′11″W.
According to the United States Census Bureau, the CDP has a total area of 2.1 square miles (5.4 km2), all land.
